summary:
The main theme or topic of this community is the development and application of language models and chatbot technologies.

Key entities in this community include gpt-4, a language model, and gpt-35, another language model, as well as chatgpt, which represents a chatbot technology that uses these language models. These entities are all related to the field of natural language processing and AI-driven communication.

The key relationships in this community involve the use of one technology by another. Specifically, chatgpt uses both gpt-4 and gpt-35 as underlying technologies to generate human-like conversations. This highlights the importance of language models like gpt-4 and gpt-35 in enabling chatbot technologies like chatgpt to function effectively.
